---
# Test-tree overrides. Inherits the repository-root policy and additionally relaxes a
# few checks that fire only on patterns inherent to the in-repo test framework and to
# the behaviour the tests deliberately exercise. The library policy stays strict; these
# relaxations are scoped to tests/ alone.
#
#   * cppcoreguidelines-macro-usage  — RADAR_TEST / RADAR_EXPECT / RADAR_ASSERT are the
#     test harness; self-registration and __FILE__/__LINE__ capture require macros.
#   * bugprone-use-after-move        — a move test intentionally inspects the moved-from
#     ManagedThread to prove ownership transferred (a well-defined query).
#   * bugprone-empty-catch           — the harness catches its own FatalAssertion to abort
#     a failed test; the failure is already recorded before the throw.
#   * readability-named-parameter    — the fallback Printer specialization intentionally
#     ignores its value parameter.
InheritParentConfig: true
Checks: >
  -cppcoreguidelines-macro-usage,
  -bugprone-use-after-move,
  -bugprone-empty-catch,
  -readability-named-parameter
...
